### ðŸ” **Analysis Pillars**

The analysis is structured around **5 key business pillars**, inspired by top consulting frameworks:

| Pillar                            | Business Question                                       | Business Impact                                           |
| --------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------- |
| ðŸ§‘â€ðŸ¤â€ðŸ§‘ **Demographic Analysis** | Which age or gender spends the most?                    | Helps target the right audience with marketing campaigns. |
| ðŸ“¦ **Product Analysis**           | Which categories drive the most revenue or returns?     | Helps optimize inventory and product strategy.            |
| ðŸ’³ **Payment Behavior**           | Which payment methods are preferred by loyal customers? | Optimizes payment UX and partnerships.                    |
| ðŸ” **Churn Analysis**             | What kind of customers churn the most?                  | Enables targeted retention and loyalty programs.          |
| ðŸ“ˆ **Trend Analysis**             | How do purchases vary over months?                      | Helps forecast demand and plan seasonal marketing.        |

